{"tid":1880243,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"各位香港市民你地好 今日掙扎咗未呢？","createTime":"2020-02-14T16:56:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T10:53:43.000Z","uid":37168,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ae21356e710d96890b395714049107f85b408d57","tid":1880243,"uid":37168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T16:56:12.000Z","msg":"首先，本教授祝各位香港市民身體健康！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/35Y5Kmo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F35Y5Kmo.jpg&h=a20d24fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係疫情咁嚴重嘅時期，除咗勤洗手同帶口罩，大家仲應該多做運動嚟吸收營養，強身健體。尤其係做阻力訓練，從而提升免疫力。<br />\n<br />\n人體入面，「精、氣、神」（健心之道之儲氣）最為重要。只要提升自己嘅「精氣神」，我地嘅免疫力自然會提升，受感染嘅機會就會下降！所以裝備好自己，我地就可以對抗疾病！！！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0UiS2MzdzY4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0UiS2MzdzY4&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNi1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=d7358b55\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0UiS2MzdzY4</a><br />\n<br />\n今日愛徒 潘師傅推肩推500磅為大家打打氣！<br />\n睇下佢幾掙扎！！！<br />\n大家一齊抗炎，一齊掙扎啦！！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Km48G6P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKm48G6P.gif&h=8adfb2c9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b7626a1e91ea852a1b5019e35adb302b39973c0f","tid":1880243,"uid":82450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T16:58:51.000Z","msg":"你瘦咗好多，無事嗎？"},{"pid":"0bf1ce0996141bd3cda59788b9713358b914a839","tid":1880243,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T16:59:04.000Z","msg":"今日淨係試咗袋底推胸同精氣元"},{"pid":"8e026f9698a7e63d4a7850515317cddf4e1c7ad9","tid":1880243,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T17:00:01.000Z","msg":"幾正面"},{"pid":"82491b5462975242a8dd6ac2220c98b26a5e733e","tid":1880243,"uid":7917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T17:01:09.000Z","msg":"胡cfu今晚有無屌女？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkg